## Dashboard Technical Specifications

### Frontend Architecture

**Framework**: React with TypeScript  
**Visualization**: D3.js, Recharts, Plotly  
**Real-time**: WebSocket connections  
**State Management**: Redux with persistent storage

### Backend Architecture

**Telemetry Ingestion**: Apache Kafka  
**Time-series DB**: InfluxDB  
**Query Layer**: GraphQL API  
**Caching**: Redis

### Performance

**Latency**: <100ms for real-time updates  
**Throughput**: 10,000+ events/second  
**Historical Query**: Sub-second for 30-day windows  
**Concurrent Users**: 1,000+ simultaneous

### Security

**Authentication**: OAuth 2.0 + MFA  
**Authorization**: Role-based access control (Observer/Steward/Forensic)  
**Encryption**: TLS 1.3 in transit, AES-256 at rest  
**Audit Trail**: All access logged in Chronicle

